EMILY MATLACK: Thank you.

00:44:13.711 --> 00:44:15.960
AUDIENCE: So you mentioned
coming out as the top thing

00:44:15.960 --> 00:44:17.584
that someone who's
polyamorous could do

00:44:17.584 --> 00:44:21.390
to help make a safe community.

00:44:21.390 --> 00:44:24.720
I've never tried
to be in a closet.

00:44:24.720 --> 00:44:30.120
But when I told my team this
week that, hey, here's a talk

00:44:30.120 --> 00:44:33.750
and you should go to it, there
were a large number of them,

00:44:33.750 --> 00:44:34.740
